data.description: Stunning home in beautiful Gates Creek! 5 plus bedroom with in-law in arrangement in a gorgeous finished basement / recreation room with 2nd kitchen. 2 separate dens on the main level (that can be turned into another bedroom) Hardwood floors, 9' ceilings, gorgeous catwalk! Neutral decor, with 42' cherry cabinets with crown molding. Granite countertops, new appliances, with a bay window in the kitchen. Beautiful master bedroom suite with sit in room, separate sinks/vanity and walk in the shower.  Newer roof, water softener, water tank & A/C.   Home is wired for surround sound and electrical in the garage for cars.  Enjoy your private backyard with an addition screened in porch and has an electric fence for dogs. So much to see, come make this your next dream home.
